relation: A coin representing two hundred dragon points.
To think such a small circular object could cause such destruction for the world. Modelled after the Canadian coin.
An object that represents monetary value for some strange reason. Save enough of them and you can buy that bicycle in the store window that you had your eye on. Or...whatever else tickles your fancy.
